title: Dope Wars 2.2 KeyGen - TUFFBUDZ
description:
Torrent contains the Dope Wars v2.2 Key Generator. You can use this app to generate a 

legit registration number for your copy of Dope Wars v2.2 only. You have to run Dope 

Wars v2.2 as an Administrator then open keygen and generate a serial. Copy and paste 

the number into the appropriate field and press enter. If you do so and you're 

getting the invalid number prompt, start a 30 day game and then enter the code 

through the "Registration" tab at the top of the window.
